Package com.microsoft.azure.management.machinelearning

This package contains the classes for AzureMLWebServicesManagementClient. These APIs allow end users to operate on Azure Machine Learning Web Services resources. They support the following operations:
  • Create or update a web service
  • Get a web service
  • Patch a web service
  • Delete a web service
  • Get All Web Services in a Resource Group
  • Get All Web Services in a Subscription
  • Get Web Services Keys
.
